version_description: Perfect fitting of chords and text pasages
Based on a guitar tutorial here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pq_mY7TVHmQ.
I've read both tabs and found one or two inconsistencies in both

I don't think they got it right. First off, non of the tabs had the right tuning. Biffy Clyro played the song in Drop C#. Version 1 was too lacking. Version 2 was just off in trying to fill in the gaps that version 1 had. I believe this is more accurate than the other tabs available.
I based this of the BBC radio's tutorial, so you can play it with open chords. With a capo on the first fret, it should be even at the proper key.
Chords suitable for beginners for this classic Biffy Clyro track. For those unable to play the full tabs available - this is just chords.
